:

1. *Gledamo* se u ogledalu. (We are looking at ourselves in the mirror.)
2. Oni *gledaju* našu utakmicu. (They are watching our game.)
3. Ona *gleda* kroz prozor. (She is looking through the window.)
4. Mi *gledamo* televiziju. (We are watching television.)
5. Oni *gledali* su film. (They watched a movie.)
6. Mi *gledali* smo šta se dešava. (We were watching what was happening.)